              <div class="pane-content">
               <div class="node node-asu-page clearfix" id="node-2">
                <h2>
                 <a href="/node/2">
                 </a>
                </h2>
                <div class="content">
                 <div class="field-asu-page-body">
                  <div class="field-items">
                   <div class="field-item even">
                    <h2>
                     Design Your Own Future
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                     <img alt="The DIY Major logo: Be individual, Be innovative, Be inspired, Be intentional, Be interactive, Be IDS" class="img-responsive pull-right" src="https://ids.appstate.edu/sites/ids.appstate.edu/files/ids_poster_logo.jpg"/>
                     Welcome!
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     The
                     <a href="http://www.appstate.edu/academics/majors/id/interdisciplinary-studies">
                      Interdisciplinary Studies Program (IDS)
                     </a>
                     is unlike any other degree program at Appalachian State University. IDS students design their own major. If you have a strong interest in integrating concepts and methods from multiple disciplines, come chat with us about options.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     We are looking for students who are
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                     <li>
                      Self-driven
                     </li>
                     <li>
                      Passionate about more than one discipline
                     </li>
                     <li>
                      Interested in a major that is not offered at Appalachian State University
                     </li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>
                     <strong>
                      <a href="https://www.appstate.edu/academics/majors/id/interdisciplinary-studies">
                       Interdisciplinary Studies
                      </a>
                     </strong>
                    </h4>
                    <ul>
                     <li>
                      2018-19 program of study, see the
                      <strong>
                       <a href="http://bulletin.appstate.edu/preview_program.php?catoid=15&amp;poid=5733">
                        Undergraduate Bulletin
                       </a>
                      </strong>
                     </li>
                     <li>
                      2017-18 or earlier
                      <strong>
                       <a href="http://bulletin.appstate.edu/preview_program.php?catoid=15&amp;poid=5733">
                        Programs of Study
                       </a>
                      </strong>
                     </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                     To Change your major, you must
                     <a href="https://ids.appstate.edu/sites/ids.appstate.edu/files/change_of_program.pdf">
                      process this form
                     </a>
                     (PDF, 162 KB) for major, minor, and catalog year changes.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     If you are thinking about changing your major to IDS and want to take an exploratory class, start by taking
                     <strong>
                      IDS 2001 (3sh) Interdisciplinary Connections I
                     </strong>
                     .
                    </p>
                    <p>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     For more information: Contact Dr. Beth Davison (
                     <a href="mailto:davisonb@appstate.edu">
                      davisonb@appstate.edu
                     </a>
                     ) or 828-262-2442
                    </p>
                    <p>
                    </p>
                    <h2>
                     Examples of Majors Designed by Our Current IDS Students
                    </h2>
                    <div class="table-responsive">
                     <table class="table">
                      <thead>
                       <tr>
                        <th>
